*Pitanje* je da li ćeš biti tu večeras? (The question is will you be here tonight?)

Ne znam odgovor na *pitanje* koje si postavio. (I don't know the answer to the question that you asked.)

Da li znaš *pitanje* koje će ti postaviti? (Do you know the question that they will ask you?)

Ne razumem *pitanje* koje si postavio. (I don't understand the question that you asked.)

Čućemo *pitanje* koje će postaviti sutra. (We will hear the question they will ask tomorrow.)